title: Impactful injuries to Derrick Henry and Jameis Winston, Cowboys call on Cooper Rush, NFL Power Rankings and MNF Preview
itunes:title: Impactful injuries to Derrick Henry and Jameis Winston, Cowboys call on Cooper Rush, NFL Power Rankings and MNF Preview
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Shaun O'Hara update the injury of Titans RB Derrick Henry. The Cowboys got a win with Cooper Rush while the Saints get past the Bucs, but have likely lost Jameis Winston for the season. The crew debates which team is the best in the AFC North while also asking which team should sit atop the NFL Power Rankings. Nate Burleson drops by plus Game Balls and a MNF preview.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
